        // ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄

        sim_layer {
            bindings = <
           &kp EXCLAMATION  &kp AT_SIGN        &kp POUND         &kp DOLLAR  &kp PERCENT    &kp CARET         &kp AMPERSAND         &kp ASTERISK           &kp PIPE           &kp MINUS
           &kp HOME         &kp DOUBLE_QUOTES  &kp SQT           &kp TILDE   &kp GRAVE      &kp BACKSLASH     &kp LEFT_BRACE        &kp RIGHT_BRACE        &kp SEMICOLON      &kp PLUS
&kp ENTER  &kp END          &kp LESS_THAN      &kp GREATER_THAN  &kp LEFT    &kp RIGHT      &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET  &kp UNDERSCORE  &hl 2 EQUAL
                                               &kp ESCAPE        &kp SPACE   &hl 0 TAB      &hl 3 ENTER       &kp BACKSPACE         &kp DELETE
            >;

            label = "SIM";
        };

        feature_layer {
            bindings = <
           &trans         &trans                &trans        &trans        &trans       &trans           &kp HOME        &kp PAGE_DOWN   &kp PAGE_UP   &kp END
           &kp C_BRI_DEC  &kp C_BRIGHTNESS_INC  &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp C_VOL_UP  &trans       &kp PRINTSCREEN  &kp LEFT_ARROW  &kp DOWN_ARROW  &kp UP_ARROW  &kp RIGHT
&kp LG(L)  &trans         &trans                &trans        &trans        &trans       &trans           &trans          &trans          &trans        &trans     &trans
